actions.message:
An Introvert Help

Hello and thank you @${tempVars("userName")} for using An Introvert Bot!
Here is a list of commands you can use.

__*Moderation commands*__

`&kick {user} [reason]`: Kicks a user from your server and tells them a reason if provided.
`&ban {user}`: Bans a user from your server.
`&mute {user}`: Mutes an user.
`&unmute {user}`: Unmutes the user if they are muted.
`&deletechannel`: Removes a channel from your server.
`%deleterole`: Removes a role from your server.

*That's all for now, more commands in the future!*
